That's it. Let's go.

36
00:03:13,800 --> 00:03:16,860
I will treat you thanking you for your surprise reaction.

37
00:03:16,860 --> 00:03:18,400
Let's go!

38
00:03:19,240 --> 00:03:20,820
Let's go!

39
