87
00:06:54,120 --> 00:06:59,480
He wanted to see me getting married very much. I couldn't make it true.

88
00:06:59,480 --> 00:07:02,960
I felt very bad the whole time.

89
00:07:07,100 --> 00:07:09,440
But now that I see you,

90
