203
00:16:09,170 --> 00:16:13,220
<i>I... I really couldn't cry.</i>

204
00:16:13,220 --> 00:16:16,360
<i>I really have to be...
- So let's get you home so you can sleep comfortably.</i>

205
00:16:16,360 --> 00:16:19,650
